---
import Page from '@layouts/page';
---

<Page title='About Nakula Dive'>
  <h1>About Nakula Dive</h1>
  <p>
    We provide dive courses and dive training. See below testimonials from our customers.
  </p>
  <div class='carousel w-full'>
    <div id='slide1' class='carousel-item relative w-full'>
      <img
        src='https://res.cloudinary.com/primayuda/image/upload/v1647237038/Nakula%20Dive/Kristina_araiwg.jpg'
        class='w-full'
      />
      <div
        class='absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 px-4 bg-gray-800 opacity-70'
      >
        <h3 class='text-xl text-white font-bold'>Kristina - Advanced Open Water</h3>
        <p class='mt-2 text-sm text-gray-300'>
          Tidak pernah sekalipun bermimpi untuk belajar diving..cuman sekali snorkelling di Bunaken ternyata membuat aku jadi tertarik untuk belajar diving. Nakula.. tahu dari teman dan sangat reff untuk belajar disitu. "kalo belajar ya sekalian yang benar instrukturnya" .. ternyata Nakula tempat yang tepat untuk diver pemula kaya aku..
        </p>
      </div>

      <div
        class='absolute flex justify-between transform -translate-y-1/2 left-5 right-5 top-1/2'
      >
        <a href='#slide4' class='btn btn-circle'>❮</a>
        <a href='#slide2' class='btn btn-circle'>❯</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div id='slide2' class='carousel-item relative w-full'>
      <img
        src='https://res.cloudinary.com/primayuda/image/upload/v1647237115/Nakula%20Dive/Andreas.jpg'
        class='w-full'
      />
			<div
        class='absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 px-4 bg-gray-800 opacity-70'
      >
        <h3 class='text-xl text-white font-bold'>Andreas - Rescue Diver</h3>
        <p class='mt-2 text-sm text-gray-300'>
          Traning to dive with Nakula Dive Center provides a fun and reassuring experience. with certified professional trainer, they sort out all the details, technical things learned and trained in respect to the safety and security. At the end, Nakula Dive Center brought me to see the beautiful blue sapphire of the sea and enjoying the amazin underwater world that can only be felt and enjoyed directly, provide and unforgettable experience.</p>
      </div>
      <div
        class='absolute flex justify-between transform -translate-y-1/2 left-5 right-5 top-1/2'
      >
        <a href='#slide1' class='btn btn-circle'>❮</a>
        <a href='#slide3' class='btn btn-circle'>❯</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div id='slide3' class='carousel-item relative w-full'>
      <img
        src='https://res.cloudinary.com/primayuda/image/upload/v1647237095/Nakula%20Dive/Deges.jpg'
        class='w-full'
      />
      <div
        class='absolute flex justify-between transform -translate-y-1/2 left-5 right-5 top-1/2'
      >
        <a href='#slide2' class='btn btn-circle'>❮</a>
        <a href='#slide4' class='btn btn-circle'>❯</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div id='slide4' class='carousel-item relative w-full'>
      <img
        src='https://res.cloudinary.com/primayuda/image/upload/v1674550902/Nakula%20Dive/Myrna_gz6pf4.jpg'
        class='w-full'
      />
      <div
        class='absolute flex justify-between transform -translate-y-1/2 left-5 right-5 top-1/2'
      >
        <a href='#slide3' class='btn btn-circle'>❮</a>
        <a href='#slide1' class='btn btn-circle'>❯</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Page>
